cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.SI 

This paper proposes a novel transformation for deep learning architectures to reach optimal cross-layer connectivity, which is a topic related to machine learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE). The paper also evaluates the proposed method on image classification datasets (cs.CV) and discusses the benefits of the small-world structure in accommodating various network architectures and datasets (cs.AI, cs.SI).
